text: Hyatt Center is an office tower in Chicago. It was completed in 2005. The 48 story skyscraper is 679 feet (207 m) tall. It is at 71 South Wacker Drive. It is owned by the Irvine Company. ==Other websites== *Emporis listing *Emporis listing for Pritzker Tower *Hyatt Center Website *Chicago Tribune - "Industry woes end Pritzker tower plan" by Thomas A.
